{"title":"瑞金与延安","authors":["王淑芬"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":8,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"瑞金与延安"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王淑芬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人说瑞金的红军井"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映着延安宝塔的倒影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今晚瑞金的红米"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与延安金黄的小米"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在同一缕炊烟里提纯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从瑞金到延安"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直线距离不过几千"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却曲曲折折二万五千里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像一条负重的扁担"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管弯曲却压不断"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心如秤星，肩是支点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六十年间不变的信念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八旬老红军新近做了个梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神思化为信念的天平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一端是瑞金，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一端是延安"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}